Price




No stock available in this market. *Estimated stock levels as of Tue, Jul 25, 2017. All items subject to prior sale. Please call ahead to verify.

 

 





Item Description

Specifications


The 5-pound Pick Mattock features a fiberglass handle. It works to loosen hard and compacted soil. Ideal for digging and chopping roots and breaking up hard soil and clay. The strong fiberglass handle won't splinter and will last for years to come. Handle guard for overstrike protectionFits #6 eye size5 -pound Pick Mattock Head.36-inch fiberglass handle





Handle Material:FiberglassHead Weight:5 lbLength:36 inType:Pick 


 
 
 

