B Holding Group, LLC

b condoms is a premium and chic socially-responsible condom company that provides a local 1 for 1 condom giveback to non-profits.






Stage

Concept Only



Industry

Consumer Products



Location

New York City, NY, USA



Currency

USD



Founded

December 2010



Employees

3



Website

bcondoms.com

















Company Summary





b condoms sells an affordable luxury line of condoms that are vegan friendly and socially-responsible. Our unique model incorporates a local 1 for 1 condom giveback to non-profits based on zip code. This differentiator allows us to have a national presence with a local footprint and distinctively compete as a local offering in the condom category. b condoms’ current income is spread among two product lines: Classic and Platinum XL sized condoms.










